These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, soy-milk
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: dubstep, reggae
1. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the fan of dubstep##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Beverage           | soy-milk | almond-milk |
| Music-Genre   | reggae     | dubstep  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
2 different pets are kept: goat, lizard
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Pet         | lizard   | goat      |
| Sport   | soccer | skateboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: photography, drawing
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, subway
1. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Hobby   | drawing | photography    |
| Transport     | boat | subway |

